{
  "meta": {
    "name": "Furwise Design System",
    "localizedName": "Furwise",
    "version": "2.0.0",
    "platform": "mobile",
    "createdAt": "2026-02-23",
    "description": "Design tokens and component specifications for the Furwise mobile application, derived from Figma design analysis."
  },

  "_mergeNotes": {
    "mergedAt": "2026-02-23",
    "changes": [
      "Border colors consolidated from 6 to 3 levels (strong/default/subtle)",
      "Text tertiary (#737373) merged into secondary (#7C6E6A) for warm tone consistency",
      "Record button text #3C3C3C unified to textPrimary #3C2E21",
      "Font size 11px merged into 12px, 15px merged into 14px (7→5 size scale)",
      "bodyName weight Bold→SemiBold, cardTitleBold removed (merged into cardTitle)",
      "Duplicate color definitions annotated with ref to source token",
      "Typography typeScale restructured from 16 semantic tokens to 7 size×weight tokens. Color removed from type tokens (determined by component context).",
      "Font families updated: Inter for Latin, 源柔ゴシック (Gen Jyuu Gothic) for CJK text",
      "Added 18 new mobile-friendly components: avatar, avatarGroup, badge, switchToggle, radioGroup, checkbox, dialog, toast, skeleton, separator, spinner, textarea, select, accordion, emptyState, slider, tabs, buttonGroup, toggle",
      "v2.0: Component specs restructured as baseline with token references for diffing"
    ]
  },

  "colors": {
    "primary": {
      "default": "#FF8000",
      "light": "#FFF3E8",
      "warm": "#FFFAF5",
      "muted": "#FFCD9B"
